N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 246.6 - Unfit food

State Regulations

No article of food shall be placed, received, or kept in
any refrigerated warehouse or locker plant unless such food is in an apparently
pure and wholesome condition. Notes
